/*
 *    Pen class.  
 */

Magnitude class Pen
"A Pen object defines the width and color of the lines
that are used to draw on a X11Pane or X11CanvasPane.
Pen objects also contain an alpha instance variable,
which can have a range of 0..65535 (0 - 0xffff), which
defines the object's opacity for drawing routines that
support alpha channel blending (e.g., the X Render library,
the GLUT/OpenGL library).";
Pen instanceVariable width Integer 1;
Pen instanceVariable colorName String "black";
Pen instanceVariable alpha Integer 65535;

